{
  "text": "This is known as the basis pursuit denoising (BPDN) in the signal processing literature [CITATION_1] . Computationally, (4) is a convex minimization problem, therefore, several fast algorithms have been proposed for computing its global minimizer, such as Homotopy or LARS [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] and coordinate descent (CD) algorithm [CITATION_4] , [CITATION_5] , [CITATION_6] .",
  "correct_citation": {
